wn18 = load_wn18()
assert len(wn18['train']) == 141442
assert len(wn18['valid']) == 5000
assert len(wn18['test']) == 5000
ent_train = np.union1d(np.unique(wn18['train'][:, (0)]), np.unique(wn18[
    'train'][:, (2)]))
ent_valid = np.union1d(np.unique(wn18['valid'][:, (0)]), np.unique(wn18[
    'valid'][:, (2)]))
ent_test = np.union1d(np.unique(wn18['test'][:, (0)]), np.unique(wn18[
    'test'][:, (2)]))
distinct_ent = np.union1d(np.union1d(ent_train, ent_valid), ent_test)
distinct_rel = np.union1d(np.union1d(np.unique(wn18['train'][:, (1)]), np.
    unique(wn18['train'][:, (1)])), np.unique(wn18['train'][:, (1)]))
assert len(distinct_ent) == 40943
assert len(distinct_rel) == 18
